# Plot
GSI_plot <- ggplot(rGSI_data, aes(x = month, y = GSI, fill = site, group = interaction(month, site))) +
  geom_boxplot(position = position_dodge(width = 25), outlier.alpha = 0.7 ) +
  labs(y = "Gonadosomatic Index (%)", x = "Collection Month", fill = "Site") +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 30)) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("#DBDBDB", "#818589"),
                    name = "Site",
                    labels = c("Arroyo Quemado Reef", "Mohawk Reef")) +
  scale_x_date(
    labels = function(x) format(x, "%b %Y"),
    breaks = seq(min(rGSI_data$month), max(rGSI_data$month), by = "1 month")
  ) +
  theme(
    panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white"),
    plot.background = element_rect(fill = "white"),
    panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "gray", linewidth = 0.5),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"),
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 14, margin = margin(b = 20)),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 35, hjust = 1)
  )

print(GSI_plot)

#ggsave("GSI Sites combined.jpg", plot = sites_GSI_combined_plot, width = 15, height = 5, units = "in")
spawn_data <- rGSI_data %>%
  mutate(month = as.Date(format(collection_date, "%Y-%m-01")))

spawn_data <- spawn_data %>%
  mutate(
    sex = tolower(trimws(sex)),
    sex = na_if(sex, ""),                 
    spawn_status = if_else(
      sex %in% c("male", "female"),
      "spawn",
      "no_spawn"
    )
  )

spawn_ratio_monthly <- spawn_data %>%
  group_by(site, collection_date) %>%
  summarise(
    n_total = n(),
    n_spawn = sum(spawn_status == "spawn"),
    prop_spawn = n_spawn / n_total,
    .groups = "drop"
  )


spawn_ratio <- ggplot(spawn_ratio_monthly,
       aes(x = collection_date,
           y = prop_spawn,
           group = site)) +
  geom_line(aes(color = site), size = 1) +
  geom_point(
    aes(fill = site),
    shape = 21,
    size = 3,
    alpha = 0.8,
    color = "black",
    stroke = 0.3
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 1)) +
  labs(
    x = "Month",
    y = "Proportion Spawned",
    color = "Site",
    fill = "Site"
  ) +
  scale_color_manual(
    values = c("#DBDBDB", "#818589"),
    labels = c("Arroyo Quemado Reef", "Mohawk Reef")
  ) +
  scale_fill_manual(
    values = c("#DBDBDB", "#818589"),
    labels = c("Arroyo Quemado Reef", "Mohawk Reef")
  ) +
  scale_x_date(
    labels = function(x) format(x, "%b %Y"),
    breaks = seq(min(spawn_data$month),
                 max(spawn_data$month),
                 by = "2 month")
  ) +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 35, hjust = 1)
  )

spawn_ratio

test_month <- ggplot(rGSI_data, aes(x = month, y = test_mm, fill = site)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = site), size = 1.5, alpha = 0.8) +
  labs(y = "Test Diameter (mm)", x = "Collection Month", fill = "Site") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("#DBDBDB", "#818589"),
                    name = "Site",
                    labels = c("Arroyo Quemado Reef", "Mohawk Reef")) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("#DBDBDB", "#818589"),  # Match colors with fill
                     name = "Site",
                     labels = c("Arroyo Quemado Reef", "Mohawk Reef")) +
  theme(panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white"),
        plot.background = element_rect(fill = "white"),
        panel.grid.major = element_line(color = "gray", linewidth = 0.5),
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        legend.position.inside = c(0.10, 0.85),
        legend.background = element_rect(fill = alpha('white', 0.5)),
        legend.box.background = element_rect(color = 'black'),
        plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 14, margin = margin(b = 20)))


print(test_month)

colors <- c(
  "ARQ" = "#DBDBDB",  
  "Mohawk" = "#818589"     
)

testvGSI <- ggplot(rGSI_data, aes(x = test_mm, y = GSI, color = site)) +
  geom_point() +  
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE, linewidth = 1) +  
  scale_color_manual(values = colors) +  
  labs(title = "GSI vs Test Diameter",
       x = "Test Diameter (mm)",
       y = "Gonadosomatic Index") +
  theme_minimal() +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(0, 250)) + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),  # Rotate x-axis labels for better readability
        legend.position = "bottom",
        plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))
